title: Astonishing Thor 01-05 (2011|Digital|Zone-Empire)
description: Fun little miniseries where Thor battles the elements gone mad in the form of natural disasters...initially thinking them to be caused by the god Zephyr, he quickly learns that much BIGGER force is to blame (think planet-sized...). Robert Rodi writes and Mike Choi draws (with a late assist from Frnak D"Armata) this simple but entertaining story. Thanks to Zone-Empire for these awesome Digital copies, please seed and enjoy! :-)
